    <item>
      <title>油价将连续第四周下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/oil-heads-for-fourth-straight-weekly-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国需求担忧持续，且 OPEC+ 准备在下个季度开始增产，油价将迎来自 12 月以来最长的周度下跌。威尔·肯尼迪在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-02/oil-heads-for-fourth-straight-weekly-decline</guid>
