    <item>
      <title>美国银行的哈特内特表示，美联储首次降息时应抛售股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/sell-stocks-at-the-fed-s-first-rate-cut-bofa-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的迈克尔哈特内特表示，当美联储首次降息时，股市很可能会下跌，因为这一转变将出现在数据显示美国经济将硬着陆而非软着陆之际。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/sell-stocks-at-the-fed-s-first-rate-cut-bofa-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息压力加大 美国债券价格领先于就业岗位价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格连续第七天上涨，因为交易员们期待即将公布的就业数据能够证明他们对于迅速连续降息的积极押注是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:41:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克期货在就业数据公布前下跌近 2%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球股市抛售加剧，纳斯达克 100 指数期货下跌 1.8%，原因是交易员担心美联储降息步伐过慢，且科技股收益令人失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国航空母公司再次放弃收购欧洲航空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iag-drops-plan-to-buy-air-europa-after-regulator-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国航空公司 (British Airways) 母公司 IAG SA 表示，由于发现监管机构的反对意见无法提供完成交易的可行途径，该公司将放弃收购西班牙航空公司欧罗巴航空 (Air Europa) 的计划，这是该公司第二次试图收购这家西班牙航空公司，但未能成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/iag-drops-plan-to-buy-air-europa-after-regulator-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
